  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Otho</b> is a male name in Westeros. Characters named Otho include:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Otho_Bracken\" title=\"Otho Bracken\">Otho Bracken</a>, a knight and Lord of Stone Hedge during the reign of kings Daeron II and Aerys I Targaryen</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Otho_II_Hightower\" title=\"Otho II Hightower\">Otho II Hightower</a>, a King of the High Tower</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Otho&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: See also\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Hotho_Harlaw\" title=\"Hotho Harlaw\">Hotho Harlaw</a>, Master of the Tower of Glimmering</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Othor\" title=\"Othor\">Othor</a>, a ranger of the Night's Watch</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Otto_Hightower\" title=\"Otto Hightower\">Otto Hightower</a>, Hand of the King to Jaehaerys I, Viserys I, and Aegon II Targaryen</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Ottomore\" title=\"Ottomore\">Ottomore</a>, a maester at Darry</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260405013318\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.003 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.003 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 3/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:32056-0!canonical an